query:
WITH inserted AS (
                    INSERT INTO category (name, created_by, color)
                    VALUES ($1, $2, $3)
                    ON CONFLICT (name, created_by) DO NOTHING
                    RETURNING 
                        category.id,
                        category.name,
                        category.created_by,
                        category.color,
                        category.last_used_at
                )
                SELECT 
                    i.id as "id!",
                    i.name as "name!",
                    i.created_by as "created_by!",
                    i.color as "color!",
                    i.last_used_at as "last_used_at!" 
                FROM inserted i
